Honors and Awards

Bradley Athletic Director's Honor Roll: Spring 2011, Fall 2012, Spring 2013

Single-Game Career Bests

Goals: 1 Three times, last vs. Northwestern (10/3/2012)

Assists: 2 Twice, last vs. Northwestern (10/3/2012)

Points: 4 vs. Northwestern (10/3/2012)

at Bradley (2010-Active)

One of 13 members in Bradley's 2010 freshman class ... His first college point was an assist on Bradley's game-winning goal Sept. 5, 2010 at Delaware ... One of five Braves to play in each of the season's first 15 games last season, Williams was the only freshman in the quintet ... Recorded a personal best of 4 points in one match by scoring once and assisting two goals in an upset of #17 Northwestern on Oct. 3, 2012 ... Bradley's active career leader in assists (10) and career games played (63).

Prep Career

Led the Lobos to Colorado state tournament semifinal appearances in 2007 and 2009, as well as a No. 2 state ranking in 2008.
